3. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking juice and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the french##1
6. the malaysian is on the far right##1
7. the italian is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
