3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person driving the bus is between the person watching romance movies and the person who likes chestnut##2
6. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the bus is the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
