.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
City: prague, nizza, edinburgh, berlin
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, funk, rock, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: german, indian, italian, mexican
1. the fan of country is the person traveling to nizza##1
2. the person traveling to prague is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the indian##2
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is the fan of funk##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the fan of rock and the mexican##2
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
6. the german is between the italian and the fan of soul##2
7. the fan of country is the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| City      | nizza | edinburgh | prague   | berlin |
| Music-Genre   | country  | funk    | rock   | soul     |
| Nationality   | mexican  | italian | german | indian   |

