The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, epic, romance, sports
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, lilac, azure, ebony
1. the person watching romance movies is the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
5. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
6. the person who likes ebony is between the person drinking milk and the person who likes apricot##2
7. the person watching sports movies is the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | hot-chocolate | milk     | tea   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | sports        | romance  | epic  |
| Color           | apricot      | ebony         | lilac | azure |

