.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-19::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, freelancer, journalist, librarian
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, baccarat, bluemaster, blend
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, scooter, subway, taxi
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the journalist##1
2. the blend-smoker is the person driving the roller##1
3. the dancer is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the subway is the librarian##1
5. the prince-smoker is the person driving the subway##1
6. the person driving the taxi is between the baccarat-smoker and the person driving the subway##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | dancer        | librarian  | journalist | freelancer   |
| Cigar       | blend | prince | bluemaster    | baccarat |
| Transport   | roller        | subway     | taxi       | scooter      |

